{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2436605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "前几期是不是难度连续偏低呀……这次难度略微高了一点。", "timestamp": 1630778959, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436612, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "e", "timestamp": 1630779148, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436622, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "bob懒得想，选择画一分钟写个程序算一下就知道了", "timestamp": 1630779426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436632, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": 2436622, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 确实这样能猜出答案——猜出来之后证明就容易了。不过不提倡这种行为！", "timestamp": 1630779639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436704, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "jifenfangcheng", "timestamp": 1630782388, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436725, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "长度为n的概率等于(n+1)/(n+1)!=1/n!（相当于长为n+1的排列前n项递增的概率），然后求期望就是e^x的泰勒展开", "timestamp": 1630783654, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436776, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1/2x2+1/6x3+1/24x4+1/120x5……=2.71828", "timestamp": 1630794848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436778, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "长度为n就是插两个点且n个点从小到大顺序排列，所以期望=Σn/C(n,1)=Σ1/(n-1)!=e", "timestamp": 1630794999, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“至少 n 个”等价于“前 n - 1 个递增”，概率为 1/(n-1)!，求期望只需全部加起来，即为 e 的定义式之一。\n优解：看到 2.7 盲猜 e。", "timestamp": 1630797078, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436797, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": 2436632, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 看选项猜答案值得提倡吗（doge）", "timestamp": 1630797200, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436817, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "重期望就完事了，记E(x)是之前最大是x的时候，到游戏停止的期望次数。那么所求就是E(0)，同时有关系E(x)=1+\\int_x^1 E(y)dy 解PDE得E(x)=C•exp(-x) 带入初值E(1-)=1知C=e", "timestamp": 1630798911, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436823, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": 2436792, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 蚌埠住了🤣", "timestamp": 1630799514, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2441062, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": 2436792, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 好像我以前的某本教辅书上有些选择题后面就会写”优解“，一般是根据选项猜出答案……\n不过还是要鼓励给出证明（笑）", "timestamp": 1630845347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2441774, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 464105, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "答案：等于 e = 2.718... 。", "timestamp": 1630853731, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 464105, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "#每晚问题 17 #数洞计划\n上期 #462664\n在区间 [0, 1] 内均匀随机选取实数，一直重复，直到某次选出的数不是已选出的所有数中最大的为止。\n例如，假设第一次选择了 0.3 ，第二次选择了 0.5 ，第三次选择了 0.7 ，第四次选择了 0.6 ，则第四次选出的数不是此时已选出的所有数中最大的，就停止操作。\n则停止时已经选出的数的个数的期望最接近", "timestamp": 1630778553, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630853734, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"2.4": 12, "2.7": 47, "3.0": 9, "3.3": 2}, "vote_options": ["2.4", "2.7", "3.0", "3.3"]}}}